assemia 8-4 其他海洋性貧血 Other Thalassemia 8-5 遺傳性血紅素病 Hereditary Hemoglobinopathies8-6 鐮狀細胞貧血 Sickle Cell Anemia 8-7 血紅素C病 Hb C Disease 8-8 血紅素E病及血紅素D病 Hb E Disease and Hb D Disease8-9 不穩定血紅素病 Unstable Hemoglobin Diseases 8-10 遺傳性高鐵血紅素血症 Hereditary Methemoglobinemia 第九章 骨髓低能性貧血 9-1 骨髓低能性貧血 Anemias of Marrow Hypofunction 9-2 純紅血球再生不良症 Pure Red Cell Aplasia 9-3 異常紅血球生成貧血 Dyserythropoietic Anemia 9-4 全血球減少症 Pancytopenias 9-5 再生不良性貧血 Aplastic Anemia 9-6 骨髓替代 Marrow Replacement 9-7 其他骨髓低能性貧血 Other Anemia of Marrow Hypofunction 第十章 大球性貧血及其他貧血 10-1 大球性貧血 Macrocytic Anemias 10-2 巨紅芽球性貧血 Megaloblastic Anemia 10-3 維生素B12之代謝 Metabolism of Vit.B12 10-4 維生素B12缺乏貧血 Anemia of Vit.B12 Deficiency10-5 惡性貧血 Pernicious Anemia 10-6 葉酸缺乏之貧血 Anemia of Folate Deficiency10-7 妊娠之貧血 Anemias of Pregnancy 10-8 出血之貧血 Anemias of Hemorrhage第十一章 顆粒球及單核球11-1 顆粒球之顆粒 Granules of Granulocytes 11-2 嗜中性球之功能 Functions of Neutrophils 11-3 嗜酸性球之功能 Functions of Eosinophils 11-4 嗜鹼性球之功能 Functions of Basophils 11-5 顆粒球功能異常 Abnormal Functions of Granulocytes 11-6 先天性顆粒球畸形Congenital Anomaly of Granulocytes 11-7 單核球之功能 Functions of Monocytes 11-8 炎症反應 Inflamemtory Reactions 11-9 先天性單核球異常Congenital Abnormalities of Monocytes第十二章 淋巴球 12-1 T淋巴球系之細胞標記 Cell Markers of T Lymphoid Series 12-2 T-細胞之功能 Functions of T cell 12-3 B淋巴球系之細胞標記 Cell Markers of B Lymphoid Series 12-4 B-細胞之功能 Function of B cells 12-5 無抗原標記的淋巴球 Null Lymphocyte 12-6 免疫球蛋白 Immunoglobulins 12-7 T-細胞及B-細胞之比較 Comparison of T cells and B cells 12-8 先天性免疫缺乏病 Congenital Immunodeficiency Disorders 12-9 後天性免疫缺乏癥候群 Acquired Immunodeficiency Syndromes 第十三章 白血球數異常之疾病13-1 顆粒球之區分 The Compartments of Granulocytes 13-2 白血球分類之意義 Significance of WBC Differential Counts 13-3 嗜中性球增多症 Neutrophilia 13-4 類白血病反應 Leukemoid Reactions 13-5 嗜中性球減少症 Neutropenia 13-6 淋巴球增多症 Lymphocytosis 13-7 傳染性單核球增多症 Infectious Mononucleosis 13-8 其他白血球增多症 Other Leukocytosis 13-9 其他白血球減少症 Other Leukopenia 13-10 脾亢進及脾腫大 Hypersplenism and Splenomegaly 第十四章 白血病之概要 14-1 白血病之病因 Etiology of Leukemias 14-